title: Yacob to miss 2015-16 season for BU
text:
Yacob to miss 2015-16 season for BU 
By wbng sports Yacob to miss 2015-16 season for BU October 13, 2015 Updated Oct 13, 2015 at 6:47 PM EDT 
Vestal, NY (WBNG Binghamton) Binghamton University junior point guard Yosef Yacob's shoulder injury will require surgery and he will miss the entire 2015-16 season, coach Tommy Dempsey announced on Monday. 
He will redshirt this year and will have two more years of eligibility left.
